com.upsight.android.persistence

Interface UpsightSubscription


  • public interface UpsightSubscription
    Defines a type which allows unsubscribing a listener from an asynchronous call.
    One of the inherent problems with listeners is that when they are called in the future, they might not be in a valid state such as when an Activity or Fragment has been destroyed. In order to avoid these listeners from being called the UpsightDataStore methods which take an UpsightDataStoreListener return an implementation of this interface in order to withdraw from being called back.
